# WaveRiders Surf Academy

A responsive multi-section website layout for a fictional surf academy.

## 📌 Features

- Navigation bar
- Hero section with background image
- About section
- Course cards layout
- Footer section
- Flexbox layout usage

## 🛠 Technologies Used

- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox)

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Open the HTML file in a browser.
2. Resize the window to test layout behavior.

## 🎯 Purpose

This project was created to practice:
- Multi-section layout design
- Flexbox positioning
- Background images
- Card-based UI structure
- Website structuring

